These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, yellow
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, scientific
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, polish, dutch
1. the person who likes orange is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the malaysian##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
3. the polish is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Color          | turquise      | orange        | yellow     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | musical       | scientific |
| Nationality         | malaysian  | polish      | dutch    |

