.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
There 3 different types of food: onion, lemon, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, coffee
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the coach##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person eating onion##1
4. the coach is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking coffee is between the person watching disaster movies and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| Food           | pomegranate  | lemon   | onion     |
| Beverage         | mirinda | coffee       | tea   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily, aconite
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
City: miami, boston, edinburgh
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person who growsaconite is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person who growsorchid is between the person watching adventure movies and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the turtle is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Flower          | aconite | orchid | lily |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Pet           | pony       | bird   | turtle    |
| City     | edinburgh      | miami   | boston |

