.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, fantasy, scientific
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, manager, police-officer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, old-henry, fonseca
There are 3 different nationalities: german, mexican, polish
1. the manager is on the left of the german##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the bartender is in an odd position##4
4. the manager is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
6. the police-officer is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the polish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Movie-Genre      | scientific     | fantasy   | western         |
| Job           | bartender | manager | police-officer |
| Cigar   | fonseca      | old-henry   | davidoff            |
| Nationality   | mexican   | polish  | german         |

