There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, italian, mexican
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the dutch is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person watching western movies is the italian##1
4. the italian is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the dutch is in an even position##4
6. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage          | hot-chocolate    | juice     | sprite |
| Sport           | water-polo | surfing | skateboarding      |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery       | disaster    |
| Nationality   | italian      | dutch         | mexican     |

