.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, metal, r&b
House: cape-cod, modern, victorian
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in the middle##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the modern house##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the fan of ambient is between the modern house and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
7. the victorian house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Hobby          | rock-climbing | singing | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action    | zombie |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | ambient   | r&b    |
| House     | victorian   | cape-cod       | modern |

