.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
City: hamburg, liverpool, colone
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, dancing, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, reggae, house
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram
1. the fan of house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
6. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of reggae and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| City      | liverpool | hamburg    | colone  |
| Hobby         | sudoku        | camping   | dancing   |
| Music-Genre   | house       | soul    | reggae |
| Transport     | tram          | quad-bike | car       |

