There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, yellow, pink
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, turkish
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, lizard
1. the colombian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
3. the turkish is the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
7. the turkish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday          | january  | march   | april      |
| Color   | yellow    | pink      | grey      |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian | turkish    |
| Pet           | lizard   | horse     | chinchilla |

