2. the person eating pepper is the brazilian##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person eating watermelon is the spanish##1

