The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse
There 3 different types of food: radish, strawberry, orange
1. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person eating orange##1
7. the fan of jazz is between the fan of punk and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | d&b       | jazz   | punk |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Pet           | bird      | chinchilla | horse    |
| Food         | strawberry  | orange     | radish |

