.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, crime
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, september, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, trike
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the trike##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre           | satire | comedy   | crime |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Birthday         | september    | february | march   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | trike     | airplane  |

