.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different games are played: go, bridge, snooker
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, photographer, police-officer
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, 7up
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, rowing
1. the person drinking tea is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the police-officer and the person playing go##2
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Game         | snooker    | bridge   | go      |
| Job           | police-officer | dancer    | photographer |
| Beverage   | tea       | milk | 7up      |
| Sport         | rowing         | parkour   | climbing     |

