The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, van
There are 3 different nationalities: french, mexican, pakistani
3 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
2. the mexican is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person playing poker is the person eating lettuce##1
5. the pakistani is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the mexican##1
7. the french is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating cranberry is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Food          | cranberry  | apricot   | lettuce |
| Transport   | subway      | van      | snowmobile   |
| Nationality   | french     | pakistani | mexican |
| Game         | mah-jongg | canasta   | poker   |

