.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, rock
3 different games are played: monopoly, go, bridge
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, writing, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person playing go##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the dancer##3
6. the police-officer is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Job           | dancer  | police-officer | musician   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock           | disco      |
| Game           | bridge   | go          | monopoly |
| Hobby     | reading    | filmmaking           | writing |

 